"        Confirmation of diagnosis",
"       </td>",
"       <td class=\"subtitle1\">",
"        Exclusion of alternative diagnosis",
"       </td>",
"       <td class=\"subtitle1\">",
"        Assessment of organ involvement",
"       </td>",
"      </tr>",
