"        </p>",
"        Viral infection (PCR for HHV-6, HHV-7, CMV, EBV)",
"       </td>",
"       <td rowspan=\"2\">",
"        <p>",
"         Blood cultures",
"        </p>",
"        <p>",
"         Antinuclear antibodies",
"        </p>",
