"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
"     * Hypoglycemic symptoms, low blood glucose levels, reversible upon glucose intake.",
"     <br>",
"      <span class=\"bullet\">",
"       &bull;",
"      </span>",
"      Diarrhea, hypergastrinemia, gastric acid hypersecretion, peptic ulcer diathesis.",
"      <br>",
"       &Delta; WDHA syndrome: watery diarrhea, hypokalemia, achlorhydria.",
"       <br>",
"        <span class=\"lozenge\">",
"         &loz;",
"        </span>",
"        4D syndrome: necrolytic migrating erythematous dermatitis, diabetes, deep vein thrombosis, depression.",
"        <br>",
"         &sect; (Questionable) elevated somatostatin serum levels, diabetes, hypochlorhydria, cholelithiasis, dia-/steatorrhea, anemia, weight loss.",
